                                            <div class="textBox">
                                                Within a few years of its inception, the Faculty of Humanities and
                                                Administrative Sciences at the University of Science and Technology -
                                                Yemen
                                                has been successful and competitive in offering business and liberal
                                                sciences programs in various specializations in Yemen, using both Arabic
                                                and
                                                English mediums of instruction. The faculty of humanities and
                                                administrative
                                                sciences has gained a robust reputation of academic excellence both
                                                locally
                                                in Yemen and internationally.Learners are equipped with skills in
                                                recognizing, evaluating and constructing arguments; reasoning; critical
                                                activity, judgement, logic and argument.
                                                <br/>
                                                <br/>
                                                Throughout its course of development, The faculty of humanities and
                                                administrative sciences-Yemen, has gone through a major restructuring
                                                exercise under the University's Strategic Plan which aimed at increasing
                                                the
                                                programmes offered. The departments of accounting, humanities and
                                                administrative sciences, represent the core domains of the faculty, and
                                                offer students the opportunity of taking a fresh look at the nature of
                                                the
                                                programmes and to explore the possibilities of making programmes both
                                                more
                                                exciting and marketable.
                                                <br/>
                                                <br/>
                                                As such, the Faculty of Humanities and Administrative Sciences-Yemen
                                                strives
                                                to offer prospective learners with accredited and up-to-date academic
                                                programmes leading to qualifications that are stimulating, and which
                                                will
                                                ultimately allow for individual intellectual growth, and at the end of
                                                the
                                                day, graduates of the fields of business administration, and social
                                                sciences
                                                are made marketable in their careers of choice, and responsible citizens
                                                in
                                                their respective societies.
                                                <br/>
                                                <br/>
                                                To this end, The Faculty of Humanities and Administrative Sciences-Yemen
                                                sets you on your pathway to shaping the future of your community. Its
                                                broad-based curricula blend knowledge with practical experience and
                                                relevance, equipping you with the confidence and skills required of
                                                careers
                                                in education and the social sciences.
